00:07:36.055 --> 00:07:38.291 line:95%,end
KELLY: Oh, well, maybe
you should get fined.

00:07:38.357 --> 00:07:42.361 line:95%,end
If I see any of that behavior,
you will leave this studio

00:07:42.528 --> 00:07:46.265 line:95%,end
